"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"With the rise of the meta universe, chain travel has once again become the focus of the encryption market. Especially in recent months, various innovative playing methods have continuously enriched the ecology of chain tourism, and the influx of traditional giants and capital has also paved the way for a wider audience. Subsequently, hot money poured into the chain travel sector, the number of users and transaction volume also achieved a breakthrough, and all kinds of tokens took off collectively.\\n\\nThe plot of the step hero game depends on the post apocalyptic war between the shadows army led by Lucifer - the demon lord and heroes led by Archangel Gabriel. Players will play the role of heroes. Their mission is to fight villains in battle and enhance their energy by collecting in-game items, making money (with step coins) and upgrading their characters.\\n\\nStep hero gamers can generate revenue in the following ways:\\n\\nIf you win the player to player (PVP) battle, you can get a reward.\\n\\nIn game items such as healing potions, power pulse potions and homemade weapons can be sold on the market in exchange for money.\\n\\nThey can upgrade their roles and trade later. The more unique and powerful their roles are, the more profits they earn.\\n\\nStep hero will conduct Ido on August 15. To participate in Ido, you need to apply for a white list. The Ido price is 0.1 $= 1hero\\n\\nThe step hero game is exquisitely designed. At present, if you want to access the official website in China, you need a VPN to log in. The built-in heroes are divided into lv1-lv4. Lv4 heroes have strong combat power and are very rare. At present, the number of step hero twitter fans is 70000 +, and the same type of imitation disk has appeared. It is hot and worth looking forward to.\",\"timestamp\":1637229056,\"title\":\"Blockchain games and meta universe are booming\"},\"digest\":\"-YcyU9a0r7GLWPbZS2pRUVKOcgE3DiokDxUG78pbI3g\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":